Website generator for http://mjhoy.com
--------------------------------------


Building

  Uses Hakyll: http://jaspervdj.be/hakyll/

    $ cd path/to/mjhoy.com/

  (Optional: set up a sandbox environment)

    $ cabal sandbox init

  Build the "blog" executable:

    $ cabal install --dependencies-only
    $ cabal build
    $ ./dist/build/blog/blog build

  Run a server (automatic re-building):

    $ ./dist/build/blog/blog watch [port]


Deploy

  Very simple: build the site and rsync the _site/ directory. See
  deploy.example for a sample script.
